  <description><![CDATA[<p>Positioned in one of Bergen's most popular areas you certainly can’t get much closer to the sites than here.</p>
<h2>Perched near the historic sites</h2>
<p>With the historic Bergen fortress to one side and Bryggen Wharf to the other, you’re sandwiched between some of the city's most popular sites. You’re within easy walking distance of many of the city's attractions and you don’t have to wander far to reach the Bergen funicular. Which whisks you up to Mount Floyen where you’ll find plenty of walking paths and wonderful views.</p>
<h2>A hotel for the perfect city (and walking) escape</h2>
<p>The hotel offers plenty of comfort with friendly service and rooms that are cosy and decorated in fresh colour schemes. People often comment on the breakfast here with the buffet offering plenty of cooked and continental delights. </p>]]></description>
